title: Growing up with a Rare Disorder (Nonspeaking and Happy)

media:group.media:title: Growing up with a Rare Disorder (Nonspeaking and Happy)
media:group.media:description:
Isabella is diagnosed with Pierre Robin syndrome. She is currently learning to communicate with sign language and also spell her name. Her family wants the world to know that Isabella brings them extreme joy and they will always love her.
